<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. صِفَاتِ مَجْدٍ وَأسْمَاءً لِمَوْلانَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تِسْعٌ وَتَسعُونَ اسْمًا غَيرَ مَا خَفِيتْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لا يَسْتَطِيعُ لَهَا الإِنْسَانُ حُسْبَانَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مِمَّا بِهِ اسْتَأْثَرَ الرَّحْمَنُ خَالِقُنَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَوْ كَانَ علَّمَهُ الرَّحْمَنُ إِنْسَانَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>نُمِرُّهَا كَيْفَ جَاءت لا نُكَيِّفْهَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بَلْ لا نُؤَوِّلَهَا تَأْوِيلَ مَنْ مَانَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَفِيهِ تَبْيَانُ إِشْرَاكٍ يُنَاقُضُهُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>بَلْ مَا يُنَافِيهِ مِنْ كُفْرَانِ مَنْ خَانَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَوْ كَانَ يَقْدَحُ فِي التَّوْحِيدِ مِنْ بِدَعٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>شَنْعاءَ أَحْدَثَهَا مَنْ كان فَتَّانَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَوْ الْمَعَاصِي الَّتِي تُزْرِي بِفَاعِلِهَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مِمَّا يُنَقِّصُ تَوْحِيدًا وَإِيمَانَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَسَاقَ أَنْوَاعَ تَوْحِيدِ الإِلهِ كَمَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>قَدْ كانَ يَعْرفُهُ مِنْ كَانَ يَقْظَانَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَسَاقَ فِيهِ الذي قد كان يَنْقُضُهُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِتَعْرِفَ الْحقَّ بالأضْدَادِ إِمْعَانَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مُضْمِّنًا كُلَّ بَابٍ مِنْ تَرَاجُمِهِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مِنْ النُّصوصِ آحَادِيثًا وَقُرْآنَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَالشيخُ ضَمَّنَهُ ما يَطْمَئِنَّ لَهُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>قَلْبُ الْمُوَحِّدِ إِيضَاحًا وَتِبْيَانَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>فَاشْدُدْ يَدَيْكَ بِهِ فِي الأَصْلِ مُعْتَصِمًا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>يُورِثْكَ فِيمَا سِوَاهُ اللهُ عِرْفَانَا<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>